{"title":"中国石匠","authors":["孙茂来"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":2,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国石匠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙茂来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国多山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛产刚硬的石匠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从古至今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石匠用钢钎和铁锤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不间断地给群山以命名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才一下子一下子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打出来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰山，华山，嵩山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山，大别山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及沂蒙山的巍峨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，老石匠们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已乘清风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相继走向群塑和碑林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的后裔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却集结到了南疆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以同样的勤恳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又凿响另一批山的英名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山，者阴山、扣林山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们的名字震撼人心"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}